You may call them like this:

```xml
<function_calls>

<call_id>$CALL_ID</call_id>
<parameters>

...

</function_calls>

```

<description>

</parameter>

<description>

<parameters>

<tool_description>

<description>

</parameter>
</parameters>

<tool_description>
<tool_name>disassemble_function</tool_name>
<description>

</description>
<parameters>

<type>string</type>
